resources.string: So that other players know who they are going to play with:
📸 your photo so that other players can recognize you on the playgrounds
🏀 Your age, height and level so that pickup games are balanced
⛹️‍♂️ Your position so that recruiters know who they are dealing with (we’ll talk to you about it when your profile is created 😉)
Are you sure you want to \nDelete Account?
Are you sure you want to \nLogout?
The court is your kingdom!\nWin games to wear the crown.
🫵 By sharing your most beautiful actions
🏀 By winning games against other players
📈 And by having the most points in the ranking!
Create matches with the ballers and become the King of your playground.
🥳Your camp is now available\n on BEBALLER
This is where you can interact with the community!
Use the + button at the bottom right to share your best plays, news, updates, or basketball articles:
To show you like a post, click on the ball.
And since we\'re all about basketball, you can give it the value of a free throw, a 2-pointer, or a 3-pointer by clicking 1, 2, or 3 times depending on how much you enjoyed the content 😉
This is where you\'ll find everything related to you. What you\'ve posted in Social, your ranking, your stats, and the badges you\'ve earned.\nYou can also change your photo and adjust your settings.
Sponsor a friend by sharing\nyour profil code
Share your profile on social medias
In the meantime, choose\nfrom those avatars
